<div class="comment-text">
<p>If you haven’t noticed that East Asians tend, on average, to excel in mathematics, you are probably engaged in motivated reasoning.  Jews have more Fields medals in mathematics than any other group.  And guess what?  Ashkenazi Jews and East Asians have the highest average IQ of any ethnic groups in the world.  </p>
